      "Basic": "Builds Authorization: Basic from username/password.",
      "ApiKey": "Injects into a default header or default query parameter depending on apiKeyLocation.",
      "OAuth2ClientCredentials": "Requests a token from tokenUrl then injects Authorization: Bearer <access_token>."
